location.fullValue: Blue Ridge Plan, The Village at Cabin Branch

data.description: Welcome to the epitome of luxury living in Clarksburg, Maryland! This stunning two-floor upper-level condo, nestled in the highly sought-after community of Cabin Branch, offers a lifestyle of convenience, comfort, and modern elegance. As you step into this meticulously designed home, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the open living spaces. The main level boasts a seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for both entertaining and everyday living. The chic and stylish kitchen features modern appliances, ample counter space, and a breakfast bar – perfect for the home chef.Venture upstairs to discover the private retreats on the second floor. The master suite is a sanctuary of relaxation, complete with a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, and a luxurious en-suite bathroom. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms offer flexibility for a home office or guest room. What truly sets this condo apart is its prime location. Situated in the heart of Cabin Branch, you're just a short stroll away from the Clarksburg Outlet Stores, providing an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Additionally, the proximity to I-270 ensures easy access to major commuter routes, making your daily commute a breeze. The Cabin Branch community itself is a haven of amenities, offering residents access to parks, walking trails, pools and community events. Imagine weekends spent exploring the scenic surroundings or enjoying quality time with neighbors. This condo not only offers a stylish and comfortable living space but also provides the opportunity to be part of a vibrant and amenity-rich community. Don't miss the chance to make this Clarksburg gem your new home – where luxury meets convenience, and every day feels like a vacation. Schedule your showing today and step into a life of elevated living!
